OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776258665
OL,3,CIrish government announces 505m euro
OL,4,Cin fuel-cost measures after protests
OL,6,FFurther reductions of duties on fuel
OL,7,Fand a delay in a carbon tax increase
OL,8,Fhave been announced by Irish premier
OL,9,FMicheal Martin after an emergency
OL,10,Fcabinet meeting agreed on a response
OL,11,Fto the fuel crisis following major
OL,12,Fprotests.
OL,14,FThe size of the package announced on
OL,15,FSunday is around 505 million euro
OL,16,F(#440 million), and comes on top of
OL,17,F250 million euro (#218 million) worth
OL,18,Fof measures announced almost three
OL,19,Fweeks ago.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
