OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776258665
OL,3,CIrish government announces 505m euro
OL,4,Cin fuel-cost measures after protests
OL,6,FThe protests ` including blockades of
OL,7,FIreland's only oil refinery and other
OL,8,Fkey depots ` strangled fuel
OL,9,Fdistribution across the country and
OL,10,Fprompted an escalated policing
OL,11,Fresponse that resulted in several
OL,12,Farrests amid clashes between public
OL,13,Forder units and protesters.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
